39 person subject to the inexperienced operator surcharge pursuant to
40 G.S. 58-36-65(k) was added has been canceled.
41 (a1) Division Records. – The Division shall ensure that its records accurately reflect the
42 insurance coverage status of: (i) each owner of a motor vehicle registered or required to be
