6 "§ 58-3-149. Certificates of insurance.
7 (a) For the purposes of this section, the following definitions apply:
8 …
9 (3) Occupational licensing board. – As defined in G.S. 93B-1(2).
10 (4) State agency licensing board. – As defined in G.S. 93B-1(3).
