1 (3) Is otherwise specifically authorized by the applicable provisions of G.S. 20-7
2 to operate a motor vehicle of the class of the shared vehicle.
3 (b) A peer-to-peer vehicle sharing program shall keep a record of all of the following:
4 (1) The name and address of the shared vehicle driver.
5 (2) The number of the valid drivers license of the shared vehicle driver and each
